Interface PwInterstitialAd.PwInterstitialAdListener

  • Enclosing class:
    PwInterstitialAd

    public static interface PwInterstitialAd.PwInterstitialAdListener
    Implement this interface to be notified of interstitial ad lifecycle changes.
